#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:193
msgid "rmw - ``rmw_init`` API Change"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:195
msgid ""
"There are two new structs, the ``rcl_context_t`` and the "
"``rcl_init_options_t``, which are used with ``rmw_init``. The init options "
"struct is used to pass options down to the middleware and is an input to "
"``rmw_init``. The context is a handle which is an output of ``rmw_init`` "
"function is used to identify which init-shutdown cycle each entity is "
"associated with, where an \"entity\" is anything created like a node, guard "
"condition, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:199
msgid ""
"This is listed here because maintainers of alternative rmw implementations "
"will need to implement these new functions to have their rmw implementation "
"work in Crystal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:201
msgid "This is the function that had a signature change:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:203
msgid ""
"`rmw_init <https://github.com/ros2/rmw/blob/"
"b7234243588a70fce105ea20b073f5ef6c1b685c/rmw/include/rmw/init.h#L54-L82>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:205
msgid ""
"Additionally, there are these new functions which need to be implemented by "
"each rmw implementation:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:207
msgid ""
"`rmw_shutdown <https://github.com/ros2/rmw/blob/"
"b7234243588a70fce105ea20b073f5ef6c1b685c/rmw/include/rmw/init.h#L84-L109>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:208
msgid ""
"`rmw_init_options_init <https://github.com/ros2/rmw/blob/"
"b7234243588a70fce105ea20b073f5ef6c1b685c/rmw/include/rmw/init_options.h#L62-"
"L92>`__"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Releases/Release-Crystal-Clemmys.rst:209
msgid ""
"`rmw_init_options_copy <https://github.com/ros2/rmw/blob/"
"b7234243588a70fce105ea20b073f5ef6c1b685c/rmw/include/rmw/init_options.h#L94-"
